01:13:15.349 --> 01:13:16.474
Psst.

01:13:16.475 --> 01:13:19.644
No one really knows Beverly
Sutphin. You see...

01:13:19.645 --> 01:13:20.846
Psst.

01:13:30.823 --> 01:13:32.782
Beverly Sutphin is insane.

01:13:33.951 --> 01:13:35.827
