01:27:53.727 --> 01:27:54.852
Hey, Serial Mom!

01:27:54.853 --> 01:27:56.061
Well, hello, New York!

01:27:56.062 --> 01:27:58.435
Beverly, who does your hair?

01:28:00.317 --> 01:28:01.442
